{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-index-js","path":"/hadoop-post-01/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Happy Hwan","author":"Hwan Choi"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"669a2013-c8a6-5a66-836c-c819437b3b60","html":"<h2>hadoop 환경설정</h2>\n<p>1> vm / 리눅스 설치</p>\n<p>-yum 업데이트 방지 설정</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/42bb7a3516ab95f305b1bf4a6b5cd4ab/14e05/ifcfg-eno16777736.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 74.45312500000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"ifcfg-eno16777736\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/42bb7a3516ab95f305b1bf4a6b5cd4ab/799d3/ifcfg-eno16777736.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/42bb7a3516ab95f305b1bf4a6b5cd4ab/00d96/ifcfg-eno16777736.png 148w,\n/static/42bb7a3516ab95f305b1bf4a6b5cd4ab/0b23c/ifcfg-eno16777736.png 295w,\n/static/42bb7a3516ab95f305b1bf4a6b5cd4ab/799d3/ifcfg-eno16777736.png 590w,\n/static/42bb7a3516ab95f305b1bf4a6b5cd4ab/2a3d6/ifcfg-eno16777736.png 885w,\n/static/42bb7a3516ab95f305b1bf4a6b5cd4ab/ae92f/ifcfg-eno16777736.png 1180w,\n/static/42bb7a3516ab95f305b1bf4a6b5cd4ab/14e05/ifcfg-eno16777736.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ul>\n<li>CentOS-Baserepo 설정</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/stati