-bottom: 77.14061272584446%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"CentOS-Sources.repo\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/440e6940a36775f4a85b2f8b9d71aba6/799d3/CentOS-Sources.repo.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/440e6940a36775f4a85b2f8b9d71aba6/00d96/CentOS-Sources.repo.png 148w,\n/static/440e6940a36775f4a85b2f8b9d71aba6/0b23c/CentOS-Sources.repo.png 295w,\n/static/440e6940a36775f4a85b2f8b9d71aba6/799d3/CentOS-Sources.repo.png 590w,\n/static/440e6940a36775f4a85b2f8b9d71aba6/2a3d6/CentOS-Sources.repo.png 885w,\n/static/440e6940a36775f4a85b2f8b9d71aba6/ae92f/CentOS-Sources.repo.png 1180w,\n/static/440e6940a36775f4a85b2f8b9d71aba6/a1c25/CentOS-Sources.repo.png 1273w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>프로그램의 소프트웨어에서 자동업그레이드 켜져있는 것들을 다 꺼주면 된다. + 소프트웨어 공급원에서 확인도 안함으로 변경하기!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>2> selinux 방지설정</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/72683ed4ccadffb4e1cf79f863e19d9e/14e05/selinx-disabled.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 77.421875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"selinx-disabled\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/72683ed4ccadffb4e1cf79f863e19d9e/799d3/selinx-disabled.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/72683ed4ccadffb4e1cf79f863e19d9e/00d96/selinx-disabled.png 148w,\n/static/72683ed4ccadffb4e1cf79f863e19d9e/0b23c/selinx-disabled.png 295w,\n/static/72683ed4ccadffb4e1cf79f863e19d9e/799d3/selinx-disabled.png 590w,\n/static/72683ed4ccadffb4e1cf79f863e19d9e/2a3d6/selinx-disabled.png 885w,\n/static/72683ed4ccadffb4e1cf79f863e19d9e/ae92f/selinx-disabled.png 1180w,\n/static/72683ed4ccadffb4e1cf79f863e19d9e/14e05/selinx-disabled.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>3> 방화벽 해제(root)</p>\n<p>systemctl status firewalld 확인후 해제</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/768c5678756e9a34acd1e3bd7394cfff/14e05/firewall_disabled.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 67.65625%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"firewall_disabled\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/768c5678756e9a34acd1e3bd7394cfff/799d3/firewall_disabled.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/768c5678756e9a34acd1e3bd7394cfff/00d96/firewall_disabled.png 148w,\n/static/768c5678756e9a34acd1e3bd7394cfff/0b23c/firewall_disabled.png 295w,\n/static/768c5678756e9a34acd1e3bd7394cfff/799d3/firewall_disabled.png 590w,\n/static/768c5678756e9a34acd1e3bd7394cfff/2a3d6/firewall_disabled.png 885w,\n/static/768c5678756e9a34acd1e3bd7394cfff/ae92f/firewall_disabled.png 1180w,\n/static/768c5678756e9a34acd1e3bd7394cfff/14e05/firewall_disabled.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>rpm -qa | grep jdk 를 하면 자바가 잡힘</p>\n<p>yum remove java 를 하면 삭제</p>\n<p>후에 다시 쳐보면 잡히는게 없다 그후에 새로운 jdk 를 설치하자.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>jdk 설치는 스킵! 압축을 풀고 환경변수를 설정하자!</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>4> hadoop 설치</p>\n<p>/root/다운로드/*</p>\n<p>/home/사용자명디렉토리/다운로드/hadoop</p>\n<p><em>우리는 완전분산 모드로 하둡을 구성한다</em></p>\n<hr>\n<p>가상머신 세개를 더 만들어주면서 network 에서 새로운 키값을 생성한다음 넣어주자.</p>\n<p>slave 1</p>\n<p>00:50:56:3F:87:A4</p>\n<p>slave2</p>\n<p>00:50:56:2E:92:37</p>\n<p>slave3</p>\n<p>00:50:56:20:EE:19</p>\n<p>gedit /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eno~~~ -> 여기서 아이피설정</p>\n<p>hostnamectl set-hostname [호스트네임]</p>\n<p>systemctl restart network 로 네트워크 다시 설정하고 조금의 시간 이후 다시 변경됐는지 ifconfig 로 확인해보자.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/91c3c55e608749a812ca9a4dfdd9bcaf/14e05/master_host.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 80%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"master_host\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/91c3c55e608749a812ca9a4dfdd9bcaf/799d3/master_host.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/91c3c55e608749a812ca9a4dfdd9bcaf/00d96/master_host.png 148w,\n/static/91c3c55e608749a812ca9a4dfdd9bcaf/0b23c/master_host.png 295w,\n/static/91c3c55e608749a812ca9a4dfdd9bcaf/799d3/master_host.png 590w,\n/static/91c3c55e608749a812ca9a4dfdd9bcaf/2a3d6/master_host.png 885w,\n/static/91c3c55e608749a812ca9a4dfdd9bcaf/ae92f/master_host.png 1180w,\n/static/91c3c55e608749a812ca9a4dfdd9bcaf/14e05/master_host.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>그후 셋다 systemctl restart network 후에 master에서 ping 으로 확인해보자</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/99a95bfbd7c80b68355f7226cfd4b6d3/14e05/network_ping.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 80%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"network_ping\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/99a95bfbd7c80b68355f7226cfd4b6d3/799d3/network_ping.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/99a95bfbd7c80b68355f7226cfd4b6d3/00d96/network_ping.png 148w,\n/static/99a95bfbd7c80b68355f7226cfd4b6d3/0b23c/network_ping.png 295w,\n/static/99a95bfbd7c80b68355f7226cfd4b6d3/799d3/network_ping.png 590w,\n/static/99a95bfbd7c80b68355f7226cfd4b6d3/2a3d6/network_ping.png 885w,\n/static/99a95bfbd7c80b68355f7226cfd4b6d3/ae92f/network_ping.png 1180w,\n/static/99a95bfbd7c80b68355f7226cfd4b6d3/14e05/network_ping.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>후에 다른 slave로 접속할때 을 할때 비밀번호 입력을 피하기 위해서 암호키를 생성하고 복사해준다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>암호키생성(참고로 root 계정이 아닌 사용자계정인 hadoop 에서 작업한다.)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/35113c8d2476551046b866b27ccc91fe/14e05/hadoop_password_make.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 80%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"하둡 암호키 생성\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/35113c8d2476551046b866b27ccc91fe/799d3/hadoop_password_make.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/35113c8d2476551046b866b27ccc91fe/00d96/hadoop_password_make.png 148w,\n/static/35113c8d2476551046b866b27ccc91fe/0b23c/hadoop_password_make.png 295w,\n/static/35113c8d2476551046b866b27ccc91fe/799d3/hadoop_password_make.png 590w,\n/static/35113c8d2476551046b866b27ccc91fe/2a3d6/hadoop_password_make.png 885w,\n/static/35113c8d2476551046b866b27ccc91fe/ae92f/hadoop_password_make.png 1180w,\n/static/35113c8d2476551046b866b27ccc91fe/14e05/hadoop_password_make.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<ul>\n<li>암호키 복사</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/stati