 relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"마스터에서 hadoop-1.21.설정\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/bfedc0f1642a22e43286bd5038d2d557/799d3/hadoop-1.21.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/bfedc0f1642a22e43286bd5038d2d557/00d96/hadoop-1.21.png 148w,\n/static/bfedc0f1642a22e43286bd5038d2d557/0b23c/hadoop-1.21.png 295w,\n/static/bfedc0f1642a22e43286bd5038d2d557/799d3/hadoop-1.21.png 590w,\n/static/bfedc0f1642a22e43286bd5038d2d557/2a3d6/hadoop-1.21.png 885w,\n/static/bfedc0f1642a22e43286bd5038d2d557/ae92f/hadoop-1.21.png 1180w,\n/static/bfedc0f1642a22e43286bd5038d2d557/14e05/hadoop-1.21.png 1280w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>요 빨간 네모들을 하나씩 수정해보자</p>\n<ul>\n<li>hadoop-env.sh</li>\n</ul>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/eafd45caec143296de7adfbbfd65d24e/14e05/hadoop-env.sh.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 80%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"hadoop-env.sh 설정\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static